{"tid":1494321,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"入籍兵艾克森：我是中國人","createTime":"2019-08-21T15:14:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T12:26:49.000Z","uid":228995,"like":5,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"fef345ef85f40801fd85793f3bf2580c1c5bdb51","tid":1494321,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T15:14:23.000Z","msg":"艾克森發表感言：我是中國人，我要回報這些年來，你們對我所有的愛和關懷<br />\n<br />\n這張照片拍攝於2013年，那時候，我剛剛落地中國。<br />\n<br />\n這是一個正在大力發展足球運動的國度，也是一個世界上很多人還不瞭解的國家，而它，只參加過一次世界盃。<br />\n<br />\n對我個人來説，這是職業生涯的一次賭博。但是廣州恆大的藍圖讓我確信，我可以在這裏寫下屬於我的歷史。<br />\n<br />\n時間過得很快。短短的三年時間，我和我的隊友們拿下了中超三連冠、亞冠雙冠王。<br />\n<br />\n我個人還兩次奪得了中超金靴的榮譽，其中一次所創造的單賽季進球紀錄，如今依然存在。<br />\n<br />\n還有2014年的中超最佳球員榮譽。<br />\n<br />\n短短的時間裏，我們贏得了如此多的獎盃。<br />\n<br />\n但是我想要一次新的挑戰，我想看看我的極限在哪裏。<br />\n<br />\n2016年，我加盟了上海上港，這是一支當時的中超新軍，雄心勃勃。<br />\n<br />\n我在上海度過了三年半的時光，116場比賽，兩個冠軍獎盃，都開創了俱樂部的歷史。<br />\n<br />\n又一次成功的經歷。<br />\n<br />\n但是我還是不滿足。因為我想回報這七年裏中國人民對我的愛。<br />\n<br />\n我在中國過得非常幸福、自在，這裏就是我的家。<br />\n<br />\n正當其時，我得知了一個非常具有挑戰意味的可能性，但是我不假思索地接受了這個挑戰。我知道，這就是我應該邁出的下一步。<br />\n<br />\n迴歸廣州恆大，迴歸這個為我打開中國這個偉大國家大門的俱樂部；加入中國國籍，讓我可以為國足再一次征戰世界盃貢獻自己的力量。<br />\n<br />\n今天，我想告訴全世界：我正式開啟了全新的征程，我是中國人，我要回報這些年來，你們對我所有的愛和關懷。<br />\n<br />\n希望得到你們一如既往的支持。<br />\n<br />\n給你們一個擁抱，<br />\n<br />\n艾克森<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.dongqiudi.com/article/1205130.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.dongqiudi.com%2Farticle%2F1205130.html&d=qWTZpUodHfCf2bB0mbfn0wRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=32491be9\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.dongqiudi.com/article/1205130.html</a>"},{"pid":"30a16a5f54c7b9fb84de6d0643b1e171875997fc","tid":1494321,"uid":234509,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T15:18:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ancMzt7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FancMzt7.jpg&h=31453b95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴西不嬲係我國不可分割嘅領土<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"084e7ae08db083eab0828087d180d413e2cbcbed","tid":1494321,"uid":200882,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T15:25:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7PZ3BKL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7PZ3BKL.png&h=30cc6756&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da08b63d81ebc2d46da5341482189f7476693660","tid":1494321,"uid":19126,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T15:25:38.000Z","msg":"艾傑臣？<br />\n<br />\n咁撚高人工你叫佢做女人都制啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c13b0be0eae3d29d1c26a92cc8386af4f9a175d","tid":1494321,"uid":44074,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T15:27:39.000Z","msg":"一條廢柴響自己國家乜都贏唔到<br />\n黎到中國贏曬啲冠軍然後仲有咁多錢收<br />\n自我感覺良好順便認埋自己係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddcf03a310762dde739a247b15986cebeca7356f","tid":1494321,"uid":228995,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"da08b63d81ebc2d46da5341482189f7476693660","tid":1494321,"uid":19126,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T15:25:38.000Z","msg":"艾傑臣？<br />\n<br />\n咁撚高人工你叫佢做女人都制啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T15:28:17.000Z","msg":"割春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就好似辛祖話我係香港人"},{"pid":"e8a98239dd97b7b5066c1b82c6ad8f5223fce15f","tid":1494321,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da08b63d81ebc2d46da5341482189f7476693660","tid":1494321,"uid":19126,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T15:25:38.000Z","msg":"艾傑臣？<br />\n<br />\n咁撚高人工你叫佢做女人都制啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T15:30:27.000Z","msg":"好撚多乞丐奶人仔奶到中共咁撚惡"},{"pid":"bcde5579a2457dafccddb37d01d9024a262d7185","tid":1494321,"uid":191811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30a16a5f54c7b9fb84de6d0643b1e171875997fc","tid":1494321,"uid":234509,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T15:18:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ancMzt7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FancMzt7.jpg&h=31453b95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴西不嬲係我國不可分割嘅領土<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T15:31:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aad78086591c9da77c493858619ae6ddfaf1f6b0","tid":1494321,"uid":60658,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:20:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZGi4muG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZGi4muG.jpg&h=f0419e84&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e540fa64b6910f11e0b5a00e577324c5b330958","tid":1494321,"uid":15830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T02:55:26.000Z","msg":"他日走資比人拉嗰陣比人他首先是中国人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4805ae96609c75f381